details.description: Innesca’s Sweets of Europe – A European-inspired bakery in Matthews, NC specializing in delicate pastries, artisanal cakes, and gourmet coffee. From French macarons and mousse cakes to classic Eastern European desserts, every treat is made fresh with high-quality ingredients. Visit us for a taste of Europe, right in the heart of Matthews downtown.

reviews_data.review_text:
Simply stunning place! All of the pastries looked so good. I got a honey cake and the strawberry raspberry mousse and ate before I could get a picture🤭

Def will be coming back.
Phenomenal European desserts and unique coffee options. Must try!

This place is amazing! I took my fiance here the day after open and we're so glad we discovered this place. Its definitely going to be our go-to. It was pretty full but we got served very fast and everyone behind the counter was super nice. Would definitely recommend
Not a big fan of coffee but the tiramisu coffee is a treat!
Loved this place. Great service and sets were awesome. Will definitely be back for more. Strawberry matcha was delicious.
Best matcha i’ve ever had like in my entire life
Best place I been in
Amazing bakery! Must try! Beautiful works of art!

10/10 all desserts, ESPECIALLY the strawberry🍓& lemon🍋 mousse cake👌🏼can’t wait to try the mango🥭

10/10 drinks as well, we got the lemonade & matcha with their freshly made strawberry puree 🙌🏼

You can’t skip it!!! Must try!!
We Visited Innascas bakery and coffee today on their opening day and oh my! Everything is so delicious! We tried a lot of pastries, desserts, coffee, matcha, energy drinks and everything was 10/10! They bake all sweets in-house. Everything is so fresh and delicious! We will be back tomorrow 😜
This place is so amazing! Such a cute place and the coffee and desserts are amazing!!! The staff is very attentive and friendly.
Such a cute place with delicious desserts and coffee ! Check out and support local
Amazing  sweets. Work of art!
Wow! We needed this!  Want to feel on vacay in Europe? This is the place. Super upbeat staff and the coffee and pastries I was hoping for. Tell ‘em “Babs” sent you! Haha!
Great service with awesome sweets will definitely coming back on a regular basis. Thank youuu

Innescas Sweets of Europe is a true hidden gem! The coffee is smooth, rich, and their pastries are absolutely delicious—fresh, authentic, and beautifully crafted. The shop has such a warm, welcoming atmosphere, and the staff are incredibly friendly and helpful. Whether you’re stopping in for your morning coffee or treating yourself to something sweet, this place won't disappoint. Highly recommend!
Staff is so friendly, and the vibe of the cafe is lovely! Amazing pastries and coffee - will definitely be back!!
Great coffee and pastries! We will definitely be back.

Came to this bakery on opening day! And the line went by so smoothly! Exceeded our expectations! We tried a variety of their pastries and we were shocked! Definitely recommend, 10/10 experience and 10/10 desserts! We also had their strawberry lemonade and loved hearing that the syrups were in House! We also tried the strawberry mousse pastry, and it was really well made and delicious, but it is on the pricier side, the quality really shows though! I’m definitely going to try the mango and lemon flavor next time! Very child friendly environment, and just awesome vibes!
Delicious pastries, super friendly staff, and a cozy atmosphere. So happy this bakery opened in town—I’ll definitely be back!

The food and coffee is the best, I want to come here every weekend so I can try everything!
I had an iced tiramisu latte and it’s my new favorite latte ever!
Delicious!!!
Wow. Amazing coffee. Amazing sweets. This place is amazing

The absolute perfect little place for the perfect dessert and coffee! I tried almost every dessert on the menu and it was an absolute delight! My favorite was the Nutella dream cake! I can eat that all day every day!
Great job God bless you 🙏
Good flavors with excellent balance of sweetness.
Best desserts and amazing drinks!
Phenomenal staff, and super friendly! I love the Matcha in the strawberry mousse cake!
This is what Matthews needed. Great coffee, great deserts.
Beautiful cafe! Pastries are beautiful and delicious. Coffee tastes great. The owners and staff are friendly and professional. This will definitely be our go to in Matthews!

review_questions.Parking options: Free parking lot, Free street parking

reviews_data.review_text: Such a cute new cafe, delicious desserts that are all homemade including the coffee syrups. Great customer service we will be back again

I stopped by this coffee shop yesterday and was absolutely blown away. The sweets were incredible, everything was made from scratch right there in-house, and you can really taste the difference. The coffee was just as impressive: fresh, rich, and perfectly brewed. It’s rare to find a spot that nails both the coffee and the baked goods, but this place does it effortlessly. Definitely worth the visit, and I’ll be coming back soon.
Great place great atmosphere, good tasting sweets. Finally, this place has something like this around.
Absolutely STUNNING! The coffee, matcha, perogi, mousse cake are ao so yummy. The quality and atmosphere of the place is lovely and homey!🍰🤩 Could not recommend it more!
Absolutely amazing 😍. I loved the food , the quality was the best I've had in Charlotte! If your in the area I highly recommend it!
